content: Today is full moon in Japan.

White can make Opening from Group of Openings
no.   White can choose Opening of the game
It was rule at that time
This is the game that Sagara and I played
I defense it.      Please think next white
At that time, I am very young player

( maybe, nobody can not find it )  ^-^
